# Pitch deck / design-handoff material at the repo root — not part of the app.
# Anchored with a leading slash so it ONLY matches the top-level folder, not the
# Flutter `features/*/presentation/` source dirs (a bare `presentation/` silently
# dropped new source files there from commits).
/presentation/

